{"source": "docs", "batch_index": 161, "chunks": [{"chunk_id": "1e781e7f934d", "text": "3. **Decorators** (Modify function behavior)", "meta": {"source": "jaseci_docs", "type": "official_doc", "upsample_weight": 3, "file": "tutorials/language/coding_primer.md", "section": "Advanced Topics to Explore", "chunk_id": "1e781e7f934d"}}, {"chunk_id": "ae89f3a54810", "text": "   <div class=\"code-block\">", "meta": {"source": "jaseci_docs", "type": "official_doc", "upsample_weight": 3, "file": "tutorials/language/coding_primer.md", "section": "Advanced Topics to Explore", "chunk_id": "ae89f3a54810"}}, {"chunk_id": "a2fe083f355a", "text": "   ```jac\n   @timing\n   def expensive_operation {\n       # ...\n   }\n   ```", "meta": {"source": "jaseci_docs", "type": "official_doc", "upsample_weight": 3, "file": "tutorials/language/coding_primer.md", "section": "Advanced Topics to Explore", "chunk_id": "a2fe083f355a"}}, {"chunk_id": "9ad9ab69398e", "text": "   </div>", "meta": {"source": "jaseci_docs", "type": "official_doc", "upsample_weight": 3, "file": "tutorials/language/coding_primer.md", "section": "Advanced Topics to Explore", "chunk_id": "9ad9ab69398e"}}, {"chunk_id": "0796f6366bce", "text": "4. **Context Managers** (Resource management)", "meta": {"source": "jaseci_docs", "type": "official_doc", "upsample_weight": 3, "file": "tutorials/language/coding_primer.md", "section": "Advanced Topics to Explore", "chunk_id": "0796f6366bce"}}, {"chunk_id": "b6a4dd8894f2", "text": "   <!-- jac-skip: illustrative; uses Python `with` syntax not yet supported in Jac -->\n   <div class=\"code-block\">", "meta": {"source": "jaseci_docs", "type": "official_doc", "upsample_weight": 3, "file": "tutorials/language/coding_primer.md", "section": "Advanced Topics to Explore", "chunk_id": "b6a4dd8894f2"}}, {"chunk_id": "cf69bb0d5557", "text": "   ```jac\n   with open(\"file.txt\") as file {\n       content = file.read();\n   }\n   ```", "meta": {"source": "jaseci_docs", "type": "official_doc", "upsample_weight": 3, "file": "tutorials/language/coding_primer.md", "section": "Advanced Topics to Explore", "chunk_id": "cf69bb0d5557"}}, {"chunk_id": "9ad9ab69398e", "text": "   </div>", "meta": {"source": "jaseci_docs", "type": "official_doc", "upsample_weight": 3, "file": "tutorials/language/coding_primer.md", "section": "Advanced Topics to Explore", "chunk_id": "9ad9ab69398e"}}, {"chunk_id": "e01c7c53acce", "text": "5. **Advanced Edge Filtering**", "meta": {"source": "jaseci_docs", "type": "official_doc", "upsample_weight": 3, "file": "tutorials/language/coding_primer.md", "section": "Advanced Topics to Explore", "chunk_id": "e01c7c53acce"}}, {"chunk_id": "13125b11fb63", "text": "   <!-- jac-skip: illustrative; `here` is only valid inside a walker ability -->\n   <div class=\"code-block\">", "meta": {"source": "jaseci_docs", "type": "official_doc", "upsample_weight": 3, "file": "tutorials/language/coding_primer.md", "section": "Advanced Topics to Explore", "chunk_id": "13125b11fb63"}}, {"chunk_id": "92a6285c74fa", "text": "   ```jac\n   # Multi-hop with complex filters\n   results = [here ->:Friend:since > 2020:-> ->:Coworker:->];\n   ```", "meta": {"source": "jaseci_docs", "type": "official_doc", "upsample_weight": 3, "file": "tutorials/language/coding_primer.md", "section": "Advanced Topics to Explore", "chunk_id": "92a6285c74fa"}}, {"chunk_id": "9ad9ab69398e", "text": "   </div>", "meta": {"source": "jaseci_docs", "type": "official_doc", "upsample_weight": 3, "file": "tutorials/language/coding_primer.md", "section": "Advanced Topics to Explore", "chunk_id": "9ad9ab69398e"}}, {"chunk_id": "b90c7dcfe614", "text": "6. **Semantic Strings** (AI-powered functions)", "meta": {"source": "jaseci_docs", "type": "official_doc", "upsample_weight": 3, "file": "tutorials/language/coding_primer.md", "section": "Advanced Topics to Explore", "chunk_id": "b90c7dcfe614"}}, {"chunk_id": "ae89f3a54810", "text": "   <div class=\"code-block\">", "meta": {"source": "jaseci_docs", "type": "official_doc", "upsample_weight": 3, "file": "tutorials/language/coding_primer.md", "section": "Advanced Topics to Explore", "chunk_id": "ae89f3a54810"}}, {"chunk_id": "5590451cf5f2", "text": "   ```jac\n   import from jaclang.byllm.lib { Model }\n\n   glob llm = Model(model_name=\"gpt-4o\");\n\n   def generate_summary(text: str) -> str by llm();\n   ```", "meta": {"source": "jaseci_docs", "type": "official_doc", "upsample_weight": 3, "file": "tutorials/language/coding_primer.md", "section": "Advanced Topics to Explore", "chunk_id": "5590451cf5f2"}}, {"chunk_id": "9ad9ab69398e", "text": "   </div>", "meta": {"source": "jaseci_docs", "type": "official_doc", "upsample_weight": 3, "file": "tutorials/language/coding_primer.md", "section": "Advanced Topics to Explore", "chunk_id": "9ad9ab69398e"}}, {"chunk_id": "19030b29cbfb", "text": "### Practice Project Ideas\n\n**Beginner Projects:**", "meta": {"source": "jaseci_docs", "type": "official_doc", "upsample_weight": 3, "file": "tutorials/language/coding_primer.md", "section": "Practice Project Ideas", "chunk_id": "19030b29cbfb"}}, {"chunk_id": "92b8d25f2b60", "text": "1. Personal budget tracker (classes, functions)\n2. To-do list manager (lists, dictionaries)\n3. Simple quiz game (control flow, functions)", "meta": {"source": "jaseci_docs", "type": "official_doc", "upsample_weight": 3, "file": "tutorials/language/coding_primer.md", "section": "Practice Project Ideas", "chunk_id": "92b8d25f2b60"}}, {"chunk_id": "42b798709ef7", "text": "**Intermediate Projects (Using OSP):**", "meta": {"source": "jaseci_docs", "type": "official_doc", "upsample_weight": 3, "file": "tutorials/language/coding_primer.md", "section": "Practice Project Ideas", "chunk_id": "42b798709ef7"}}, {"chunk_id": "d2397ec03180", "text": "1. Family tree explorer (nodes, edges, walkers)\n2. Course planner with prerequisites (graph queries)\n3. Social network analyzer (bidirectional relationships)\n4. Recommendation engine (graph traversal)", "meta": {"source": "jaseci_docs", "type": "official_doc", "upsample_weight": 3, "file": "tutorials/language/coding_primer.md", "section": "Practice Project Ideas", "chunk_id": "d2397ec03180"}}, {"chunk_id": "f32817dfd39f", "text": "**Advanced Projects:**", "meta": {"source": "jaseci_docs", "type": "official_doc", "upsample_weight": 3, "file": "tutorials/language/coding_primer.md", "section": "Practice Project Ideas", "chunk_id": "f32817dfd39f"}}, {"chunk_id": "47e40e65939e", "text": "1. Knowledge graph for a specific domain\n2. Workflow automation system\n3. Route planner for transportation\n4. Content recommendation system", "meta": {"source": "jaseci_docs", "type": "official_doc", "upsample_weight": 3, "file": "tutorials/language/coding_primer.md", "section": "Practice Project Ideas", "chunk_id": "47e40e65939e"}}, {"chunk_id": "df0050cf9c2b", "text": "### Learning Resources\n\n**Within this Repository:**", "meta": {"source": "jaseci_docs", "type": "official_doc", "upsample_weight": 3, "file": "tutorials/language/coding_primer.md", "section": "Learning Resources", "chunk_id": "df0050cf9c2b"}}, {"chunk_id": "ae3f2e4e2940", "text": "- `/jac/examples/reference/` - All the detailed reference examples\n- Look for `*.md` files for explanations\n- Look for `*.jac` files for code examples", "meta": {"source": "jaseci_docs", "type": "official_doc", "upsample_weight": 3, "file": "tutorials/language/coding_primer.md", "section": "Learning Resources", "chunk_id": "ae3f2e4e2940"}}, {"chunk_id": "7f0712dbe4c6", "text": "**Key Files to Explore:**", "meta": {"source": "jaseci_docs", "type": "official_doc", "upsample_weight": 3, "file": "tutorials/language/coding_primer.md", "section": "Learning Resources", "chunk_id": "7f0712dbe4c6"}}, {"chunk_id": "282b5bb7a865", "text": "- `archetypes.md` - Deep dive into obj, node, edge, walker\n- `object_spatial_*.md` - Advanced OSP features\n- `match_statements.md` - Pattern matching\n- `functions_and_abilities.md` - Function deep dive", "meta": {"source": "jaseci_docs", "type": "official_doc", "upsample_weight": 3, "file": "tutorials/language/coding_primer.md", "section": "Learning Resources", "chunk_id": "282b5bb7a865"}}, {"chunk_id": "24c58b30c2a9", "text": "### Final Thoughts\n\nYou've learned two paradigms:", "meta": {"source": "jaseci_docs", "type": "official_doc", "upsample_weight": 3, "file": "tutorials/language/coding_primer.md", "section": "Final Thoughts", "chunk_id": "24c58b30c2a9"}}, {"chunk_id": "42cf33e524e3", "text": "1. **Traditional programming** (variables → functions → classes)\n2. **Object-Spatial Programming** (nodes → edges → walkers)", "meta": {"source": "jaseci_docs", "type": "official_doc", "upsample_weight": 3, "file": "tutorials/language/coding_primer.md", "section": "Final Thoughts", "chunk_id": "42cf33e524e3"}}, {"chunk_id": "df794f1b3768", "text": "This makes you uniquely prepared to:", "meta": {"source": "jaseci_docs", "type": "official_doc", "upsample_weight": 3, "file": "tutorials/language/coding_primer.md", "section": "Final Thoughts", "chunk_id": "df794f1b3768"}}, {"chunk_id": "d1de487bd0c4", "text": "- Build traditional applications (like Python, Java, JavaScript)\n- Build graph-based applications (social networks, knowledge graphs, recommendation systems)\n- Think about data and computation in revolutionary new ways", "meta": {"source": "jaseci_docs", "type": "official_doc", "upsample_weight": 3, "file": "tutorials/language/coding_primer.md", "section": "Final Thoughts", "chunk_id": "d1de487bd0c4"}}, {"chunk_id": "9b75062c6c7a", "text": "**The key insight of OSP:**\n> \"Don't bring data to computation. Send computation to where the data lives.\"", "meta": {"source": "jaseci_docs", "type": "official_doc", "upsample_weight": 3, "file": "tutorials/language/coding_primer.md", "section": "Final Thoughts", "chunk_id": "9b75062c6c7a"}}, {"chunk_id": "61a031ef2b54", "text": "This simple idea unlocks powerful new ways to solve problems, especially when data has complex relationships.", "meta": {"source": "jaseci_docs", "type": "official_doc", "upsample_weight": 3, "file": "tutorials/language/coding_primer.md", "section": "Final Thoughts", "chunk_id": "61a031ef2b54"}}, {"chunk_id": "11e840c6e7a9", "text": "Keep practicing, keep building, and welcome to the world of programming!", "meta": {"source": "jaseci_docs", "type": "official_doc", "upsample_weight": 3, "file": "tutorials/language/coding_primer.md", "section": "Final Thoughts", "chunk_id": "11e840c6e7a9"}}, {"chunk_id": "9b848fe603ab", "text": "---", "meta": {"source": "jaseci_docs", "type": "official_doc", "upsample_weight": 3, "file": "tutorials/language/coding_primer.md", "section": "Final Thoughts", "chunk_id": "9b848fe603ab"}}, {"chunk_id": "aebe07983631", "text": "## Appendix: Quick Reference", "meta": {"source": "jaseci_docs", "type": "official_doc", "upsample_weight": 3, "file": "tutorials/language/coding_primer.md", "section": "Appendix: Quick Reference", "chunk_id": "aebe07983631"}}, {"chunk_id": "4512a5bab6d6", "text": "### Basic Syntax\n\n<div class=\"code-block\">", "meta": {"source": "jaseci_docs", "type": "official_doc", "upsample_weight": 3, "file": "tutorials/language/coding_primer.md", "section": "Basic Syntax", "chunk_id": "4512a5bab6d6"}}, {"chunk_id": "0fc9bf7305e8", "text": "```jac\n# Comments\n# Single line comment\n#* Multi-line\n   comment *#\n\n# Entry point\nwith entry {\n    # Statements end with semicolons\n    x = 5;\n    print(x);\n\n    # Blocks use curly braces\n    if x > 0 {\n        print(\"positive\");\n    }\n}\n```", "meta": {"source": "jaseci_docs", "type": "official_doc", "upsample_weight": 3, "file": "tutorials/language/coding_primer.md", "section": "Basic Syntax", "chunk_id": "0fc9bf7305e8"}}, {"chunk_id": "e6e034754912", "text": "</div>", "meta": {"source": "jaseci_docs", "type": "official_doc", "upsample_weight": 3, "file": "tutorials/language/coding_primer.md", "section": "Basic Syntax", "chunk_id": "e6e034754912"}}, {"chunk_id": "1c221cda83e4", "text": "### Data Types\n\n<div class=\"code-block\">", "meta": {"source": "jaseci_docs", "type": "official_doc", "upsample_weight": 3, "file": "tutorials/language/coding_primer.md", "section": "Data Types", "chunk_id": "1c221cda83e4"}}, {"chunk_id": "879763fadb7c", "text": "```jac\nwith entry {\n    # Primitives\n    name: str = \"Alice\";\n    age: int = 25;\n    height: float = 5.6;\n    is_student: bool = True;\n\n    # Collections\n    numbers: list = [1, 2, 3];\n    coords: tuple = (10, 20);\n    person: dict = {\"name\": \"Alice\", \"age\": 25};\n    unique: set = {1, 2, 3};\n\n    print(f\"Name: {name}, Age: {age}\");\n    print(f\"Numbers: {numbers}\");\n}\n```", "meta": {"source": "jaseci_docs", "type": "official_doc", "upsample_weight": 3, "file": "tutorials/language/coding_primer.md", "section": "Data Types", "chunk_id": "879763fadb7c"}}, {"chunk_id": "07ab0358c773", "text": "</div>", "meta": {"source": "jaseci_docs", "type": "official_doc", "upsample_weight": 3, "file": "tutorials/language/coding_primer.md", "section": "Data Types", "chunk_id": "07ab0358c773"}}, {"chunk_id": "ab857991b625", "text": "### Control Flow\n\n<div class=\"code-block\">", "meta": {"source": "jaseci_docs", "type": "official_doc", "upsample_weight": 3, "file": "tutorials/language/coding_primer.md", "section": "Control Flow", "chunk_id": "ab857991b625"}}, {"chunk_id": "243769072163", "text": "```jac\nwith entry {\n    # If statement\n    condition = True;\n    other_condition = False;\n    if condition {\n        print(\"Condition is true\");\n    } elif other_condition {\n        print(\"Other condition is true\");\n    } else {\n        print(\"Neither condition is true\");\n    }\n\n    # While loop\n    count = 0;\n    while count < 3 {\n        print(f\"Count: {count}\");\n        count += 1;\n    }\n\n    # For loop (counting)\n    for i = 0 while i < 5 with i += 1 {\n        print(f\"i: {i}\");\n    }\n\n    # For loop (iteration)\n    collection = [\"a\", \"b\", \"c\"];\n    for item in collection {\n        print(f\"Item: {item}\");\n    }\n}\n```", "meta": {"source": "jaseci_docs", "type": "official_doc", "upsample_weight": 3, "file": "tutorials/language/coding_primer.md", "section": "Control Flow", "chunk_id": "243769072163"}}, {"chunk_id": "e29ca2f16c8f", "text": "</div>", "meta": {"source": "jaseci_docs", "type": "official_doc", "upsample_weight": 3, "file": "tutorials/language/coding_primer.md", "section": "Control Flow", "chunk_id": "e29ca2f16c8f"}}, {"chunk_id": "8f69a6fedd9b", "text": "### Functions\n\n<div class=\"code-block\">", "meta": {"source": "jaseci_docs", "type": "official_doc", "upsample_weight": 3, "file": "tutorials/language/coding_primer.md", "section": "Functions", "chunk_id": "8f69a6fedd9b"}}, {"chunk_id": "fa6130467fbc", "text": "```jac\n# Basic function\ndef greet(name: str) {\n    print(f\"Hello, {name}!\");\n}\n\n# With return value\ndef add(x: int, y: int) -> int {\n    return x + y;\n}\n\n# With default parameters\ndef greet_default(name: str = \"friend\") {\n    print(f\"Hello, {name}!\");\n}\n\nwith entry {\n    greet(\"Alice\");\n    result = add(5, 3);\n    print(f\"5 + 3 = {result}\");\n    greet_default();\n    greet_default(\"Bob\");\n}\n```", "meta": {"source": "jaseci_docs", "type": "official_doc", "upsample_weight": 3, "file": "tutorials/language/coding_primer.md", "section": "Functions", "chunk_id": "fa6130467fbc"}}, {"chunk_id": "3e3be6440d4b", "text": "</div>", "meta": {"source": "jaseci_docs", "type": "official_doc", "upsample_weight": 3, "file": "tutorials/language/coding_primer.md", "section": "Functions", "chunk_id": "3e3be6440d4b"}}, {"chunk_id": "062b2dd089c7", "text": "### Classes\n\n<div class=\"code-block\">", "meta": {"source": "jaseci_docs", "type": "official_doc", "upsample_weight": 3, "file": "tutorials/language/coding_primer.md", "section": "Classes", "chunk_id": "062b2dd089c7"}}, {"chunk_id": "89798751335c", "text": "```jac\nobj MyClass {\n    has property: str;\n\n    def method {\n        print(self.property);\n    }\n}\n\nwith entry {\n    my_obj = MyClass(property=\"Hello, World!\");\n    my_obj.method();\n}\n```", "meta": {"source": "jaseci_docs", "type": "official_doc", "upsample_weight": 3, "file": "tutorials/language/coding_primer.md", "section": "Classes", "chunk_id": "89798751335c"}}, {"chunk_id": "caab0bc7bb00", "text": "</div>", "meta": {"source": "jaseci_docs", "type": "official_doc", "upsample_weight": 3, "file": "tutorials/language/coding_primer.md", "section": "Classes", "chunk_id": "caab0bc7bb00"}}], "near_dup_candidates": []}